<refsect2 id="gtk-clutter-viewport-get-origin" role="function" condition="since:0.10">
<title>gtk_clutter_viewport_get_origin ()</title>
<indexterm zone="gtk-clutter-viewport-get-origin" role="0.10"><primary sortas="viewport_get_origin">gtk_clutter_viewport_get_origin</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>                gtk_clutter_viewport_get_origin     (<link linkend="GtkClutterViewport">GtkClutterViewport</link> *viewport,
                                                         <link linkend="gfloat">gfloat</link> *x,
                                                         <link linkend="gfloat">gfloat</link> *y,
                                                         <link linkend="gfloat">gfloat</link> *z);</programlisting>
<para>
Retrieves the current translation factor ("origin") used when
displaying the child of <parameter>viewport</parameter>.</para>
<para>
</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>viewport</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> a <link linkend="GtkClutterViewport"><type>GtkClutterViewport</type></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>x</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> return location for the X origin in pixels, or <link linkend="NULL--CAPS"><literal>NULL</literal></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>y</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> return location for the Y origin in pixels, or <link linkend="NULL--CAPS"><literal>NULL</literal></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>z</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> return location for the Z origin in pixels, or <link linkend="NULL--CAPS"><literal>NULL</literal></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist><para role="since">Since 0.10</para></refsect2>

</refsect1>
